Maintainer: Dario Griffo <dariogriffo@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://code.forgejo.org/forgejo/runner
Package: forgejo-runner
Version: FORGEJO_RUNNER_VERSION-BUILD_VERSION~DIST
Architecture: SUPPORTED_ARCHITECTURES
Depends: adduser
Description: Runner for Forgejo Actions
 forgejo-runner is the task runner for Forgejo Actions, the CI/CD
 system built into Forgejo. It registers against a Forgejo instance
 and executes the workflow jobs it is assigned.
